title: Criminal Macabre Omnibus V1 (2011) (digital)
description:
So hesitant upload something that's here numerous times already... however, A) this looks tits, and B) this book has issues 4-5 of Supernatural Freak Machine, which I don't think has been previously uploaded (apologies if it has).

-------------------------------------------------------

Criminal Macabre Omnibus Volume 1

Dark Horse, 2011, 380 pages

Written and Illustrated by Steve Niles, Ben Templesmith, Kelley Jones, Michelle Madsen, Nate Piekos of Blambot, Pat Brosseau, Tom B Long

This volume collects Criminal McCabre - A Cal McDonald Mystery 1-5, A Letter From BS, Love Me Tenderloin, Last Train To Deadsville 1-4, Supernatural Freak Machine 1-5 (issues 4-5 of SFM unpublished prior to this release)
